_xResult.title: Woo Me Dress
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made wool dress with belt
_xResult.longdesc:
This custom made wool dress, perfect for fall or winter, is a casual black masterpiece with an asymmetric and extravagant fit. We’re going crazy for the wide sleeves and elegant belt. This made to measure dress is perfect for anyone who wants to be different. Best of all, it has a very warm and soft feeling when you slip it on.

 

Have fun with EUG's custom made designer clothing! For custom made requests regarding sizing, let the designer know using the button below.
